stix:STIX_Header.stix:Title: Compromised Nodes Used for Malicious Activity
stix:STIX_Header.stix:Description: A trusted third party has found these IP addresses to be conducting malicious activity. It is likely that these nodes were compromised and are being used as a hop-point to mask the identity of the malicious actor. The owner of the nodes may not be aware that the malicious activity is occurring.

stix:Indicator.indicator:Title: Malicious IPv4 Indicator
stix:Indicator.indicator:Description: This IP is a node being used as a hop-point to conduct malicious activity.
